---
title: Asian Pork Schnitzel & Ginger-Coconut Sauce with Jasmine Rice & Rainbow Slaw
description: Steamed rice provides the perfect base for panko-crumbed pork and a rainbow pear slaw that'll have you experiencing a magical fusion
feast with ease. For the big finish, pull the rabbit out of the hat by topping your pork with a creamy ginger-infused coconut sauce. Tada!
